      "item": "resolve_with_injection",
      "reviewed": true,
      "intent": "Handle injection-enabled tree_path resolution. Resolve host-side segments to the injection-point node, extract the injected content from the YAML value, sub-parse it with the injected language's grammar, and resolve remaining inner segments. Translate inner spans back to outer-file coordinates by adding the line offset. Returns the full injected content span if no inner segments follow the //lang marker.",
